=== Noun ===
'''smell''' (''countable''; ''plural:'' [[smells]])

#The [[scent]] [[give off|given off]] by something.
#:''I love the smell of fresh bread.''

====Synonyms====
*[[aroma]] (1)
*[[odour]] (1)
*[[scent]] (1)

